<![CDATA[<div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://c.na8.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015C0000002uJCs&amp;oid=00D80000000ZK1f&amp;lastMod=1456855016000" alt="Right click on the image to save it to your computer."></div><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></font></div></font><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;">Hey {!Contact.FirstName}!</div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><b>Congratulations on securing a place to volunteer alongside the NCS Trust and Santander this Friday - competition was tight, so we're delighted to be able to invite you along.</b></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;">Before you come you need to fill out <a href="https://docs.google.com/a/the-challenge.org/forms/d/17Z5IpiccizYlKfLzez8Cn_vU7yvGZ5th1gojgYNIm2M/viewform"><b>this short form</b></a>&nbsp;by <b>6pm tomorrow</b>&nbsp;- if you have any problems getting that done then give me a call or text on <b>07587 037601</b>.</div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;">Attached is a letter that you can give to your teachers to explain your absence. Again, any problems either you or your teacher can give me a call to discuss the day.</div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><b>Make sure you really think about any questions you might want to ask the professionals who are also volunteering with you on Friday - they have absolutely loads of experience and knowledge in all different areas, so make good use of the chance to talk to them and get networking.</b></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">See you on Friday!</span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Megan</span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#cc0000"><b><a href="http://tcsnorthlondon.co.uk/"><br></a></b></font></span></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"></div><div><div style="text-align: center;"><font face="arial" color="#cc0000"><b><a href="http://tcsnorthlondon.co.uk/">WWW.TCSNORTHLONDON.CO.UK</a></b></font><br><br></div></div>]]></td>
